The '''Diokno Highway''' is a {{convert|20.068|km|mi|adj=on}}, two lane, secondary road in the provinces of [[Cavite]] and [[Batangas]] that connects the municipality of [[Alfonso, Cavite|Alfonso]] in Cavite and the municipality of [[Lemery, Batangas|Lemery]] in Batangas.<ref name="atlas">{{cite web|url=http://www.dpwh.gov.ph/dpwh/2016%20DPWH%20ATLAS/Road%20Data%202016/cavite.htm |title=2016 DPWH Road Data |publisher=[[Department of Public Works and Highways (Philippines)|Department of Public Works and Highways]] |accessdate=8 March 2018}}</ref> It runs in southern [[Cavite]] to [[Batangas]].
