{{about|the suburb of Zagreb|the village near Novi Marof|Remetinec, Varaždin County}}

'''Remetinec''' is a neighborhood in the [[Novi Zagreb &ndash; zapad]] city district of [[Zagreb]], the capital of [[Croatia]]. It is located south of the [[Remetinec Roundabout]] and [[Lanište, Croatia|Lanište]], west of [[Trokut]] and the railway triangle and west of [[Blato, Zagreb|Blato]]. It has a population of 4,271 (2011).<ref>http://www.zagreb.hr/default.aspx?id=15055</ref>

