{{Infobox settlement | name = Sur del Lago de Maracaibo | native_name = | other_name = Sur del Lago | settlement_type = [[Regions of Venezuela|Subregión]] <!-- images, nickname, motto --> | image_skyline = Catatumbolightning.jpg | image_caption = View of [[Catatumbo lightning]], Zulia | image_flag = | image_shield = | motto = | nickname = | etymology = <!-- location --> | subdivision_type = Country | subdivision_name = Venezuela | subdivision_type1 = | subdivision_name1 = | subdivision_type2 = Region | subdivision_name2 = [[Zulia]] | subdivision_type3 = | subdivision_name3 = | subdivision_type4 = | subdivision_name4 = <!-- maps and coordinates --> | image_map = Venezuela - Zulia - Sur del Lago.svg | map_caption = Approximate extent of Sur del Lago | pushpin_map = | pushpin_relief = | pushpin_map_caption = | coordinates = {{coord|9|N|73|W|display=inline,title}} | coordinates_footnotes = <!-- established --> | established_title = | established_date = <!-- area --> | area_footnotes = | area_total_km2 = 18440 | area_total_sq_mi = | area_land_sq_mi = | area_water_sq_mi = <!-- elevation --> | elevation_footnotes = | elevation_m = | elevation_ft = <!-- population --> | population_as_of = 2012 | population_footnotes = | population_total = 624,177 | population_density_km2 = auto | population_density_sq_mi= | population_demonym = <!-- time zone(s) --> | timezone1 = | utc_offset1 = | timezone1_DST = | utc_offset1_DST = <!-- postal codes, area code --> | postal_code_type = | postal_code = | area_code_type = | area_code = | geocode = | iso_code = <!-- website, footnotes --> | website = | footnotes = }}
'''Sur del Lago de Maracaibo''' (often abbreviated as '''Sur del Lago''', in English '''''South of Maracaibo Lake''''') is a subregion comprising the territory of the municipalities [[w:es:Jesús María Semprún (Zulia)|Jesús María Semprún]], [[w:es:Municipio Catatumbo|Catatumbo]], [[w:es:Municipio Colón (Zulia)|Colón]], [[w:es:Municipio Francisco Javier Pulgar|Francisco Javier Pulgar]] and [[w:es:Sucre (Zulia)|Sucre]] from [[Zulia]] state and the municipality [[Alberto Adriani Municipality|Alberto Adriani]], [[Obispo Ramos de Lora Municipality|Obispo Ramos Lora]] and the population of [[w:es:Palmarito (Mérida)|Palmarito]] from [[w:es:Tulio Febres Cordero (municipio)|Tulio Febres Cordero municipality]] from the state of [[Mérida state|Mérida]], Venezuela. Its major towns are [[Santa Barbara del Zulia]], [[San Carlos del Zulia]] and [[w:es:El Vigía|El Vigia]], which represents its economic epicenter.
